Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:05.48,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Vamos viajar por todos os mares do mundo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:07.85,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,levantando nosso grito de guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:12.19,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se você já se decidiu, deixe o sinal de partida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.63,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,soar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:25.34,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos escapar do curso definido
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:28.77,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,ao longo da fronteira entre o céu e o mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:34.15,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Agora estamos remando em nosso caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:40.55,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,para uma aventura escondida no fundo escuro do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:47.49,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Não parece divertido só de pensar nisso?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:51.96,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vamos viajar por todos os mares do mundo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:54.23,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,levantando nosso grito de guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.57,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se você já se decidiu, deixe o sinal para a partida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:01.01,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,soar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:11.58,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Aquela sensação que tivemos quando zarpamos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:15.05,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,é algo que nunca esquecerei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:16.72,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Por causa disso
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:20.53,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,nada vai me assustar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:26.77,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Agora, conforme a viagem se aproxima, nossos batimentos cardíacos acelerados
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:33.84,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,gravam um ritmo de aventura em nossos corações tímidos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:38.11,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Pegue todos os tesouros
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.41,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,enquanto ri alto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:44.85,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,50)}Então distribua tudo em uma grande festa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:47.35,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,fazendo barulho...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.50,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,A vida é uma aventura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:51.00,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Fica ligado, que é perigosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.50,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Quem será um de nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.50,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,E a viagem segue porque
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.00,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Somos os piratas do povo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:57.80,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Para o oeste! Para o leste!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:00.30,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vou traçar minha rota e navegar até o One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:04.60,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Encha seu coração vazio com sonhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.91,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Abra suas asas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:11.31,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Se você colorir seu coração com o vento soprando
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.65,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,você seguirá em frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:17.72,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,Pegue todos os tesouros
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:20.09,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(60,0)}enquanto ri alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:24.49,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,então distribua tudo em uma grande festa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.23,Jungle P lyrics,,0,0,0,,fazendo barulho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:38.52,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}Aniquilação da Tripulação! Oars vs. Luffy Pesadelp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.21,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Hōrudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.21,Note,Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Segurar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.58,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Eu não posso{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.55,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:56.10,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,É assim que você pretende me impedir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:59.72,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Que ato sem sentido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.74,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Burikku Batto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.74,Note,Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Morcegos de Fragmentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:10.99,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.69,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Veinte Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.66,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kandyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.45,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:30.59,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Como ousa machucar Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.94,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,A sombra de Moriah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.41,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Agora, vamos lutar para decidir qual é a melhor habilidade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.48,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Esse seu golpe é bem efetivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.77,Thoughts,Robin,0,0,0,,Eu não deveria prestar atenção à sombra dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.40,Thoughts,Robin,0,0,0,,Se eu derrubar o corpo, a sombra certamente será aniquilada também.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:07.96,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kuwatoro Mānosu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:07.96,Note,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Quatro Árvores!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:13.44,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,E-Ei, você!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.61,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,O que você está{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.98,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:16.99,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kuracchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:16.99,Note,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Apertão!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ela conseguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.76,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Você é incrível, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.48,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Ei, Robin! Cuidado com a sombra atrás de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.76,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,O que Moriah está fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.48,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Bem perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.85,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Mas é uma pena para você,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:52.04,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Eu posso trocar de lugar com Doppelman quando eu quiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.24,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Trocar de lugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.78,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Então, aquele ali é...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.75,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Sua chave de braço não vai funcionar na minha sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:06.53,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Sim, a mesma sombra que estava aqui há um tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.43,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Robin-cha{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.46,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Agora são três a menos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A sombra da Robin também foi levada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:40.02,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Não tenho uma marionete para você agora, então posso deixá-lo comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.71,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Diaburu Janbu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.11,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Seu bastardo imundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.22,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Devolva a sombra da Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.32,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ekusutora Asshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.71,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Burikku Batto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.61,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Ele trocou de lugar com sua sombra de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.29,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Então, isso significa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:17.52,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Moriah está de volta ao estômago de Oars novamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.30,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,E agora você está de volta onde começou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:25.40,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Droga, Mestre!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.30,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Pare de atrapalhar minha luta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.02,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Minha culpa, Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.24,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Parece que me empolguei um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:36.34,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,É melhor eu acabar com aquela mulher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:40.46,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ele consegue se esticar de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.13,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Robin não está mais consciente!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.96,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Sanji! Robin! Corra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.28,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bazūka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:57.13,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Diaburu Janbu... 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.92,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Furitto Asoruti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.24,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ele desviou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Agora é nossa chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.52,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Leve a Robin-chan embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.65,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.47,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:24.71,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.66,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.56,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Chopper, o que? o que você está fazendo aí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:35.40,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Eu estava procurando a causa da morte de Oars quinhentos anos atrás.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:37.87,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Causa da morte?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.65,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Foquem o ataque no seu braço direito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.24,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Este não é o braço original de Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.02,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Embora tenha sido restaurado pelas incríveis habilidades de Hogback,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07: 48.01,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,As juntas mostram restos de congelamento terrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.06,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Não tenho certeza, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.72,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,A causa de sua morte, 500 anos atrás, foi provavelmente congelamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.05,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Apesar de ser um monstro, ele não era páreo para as forças da natureza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:01.03,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Ele congelou até a morte enquanto vagava pelo País do Gelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:05.06,Main, Chopper,0,0,0,,A razão é que, mesmo quinhentos anos atrás, Oars andava...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.22,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Nu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.27,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Não acredito que estamos perdendo para um idiota desses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.85,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Zumbis podem não sentir dor, mas o dano recebido permanece.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:17.84,Main,Chopper, 0,0,0,,Todos os ataques que ele recebeu foram se acumulando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:22.81,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Se nos livrarmos desse braço, sua força será reduzida pela metade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, mirem neste ponto{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:30.15,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Pare de tagarelar, seu homenzinho no meu ombro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.99,Main,Zoro,0 ,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:45.54,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Um zumbi como você nem consegue perceber o quanto aquele soco agora machucou seu corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.41,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Ele está na minha mão.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:54.67,Main, Chopper,0,0,0,,Com meu tamanho atual, o vão no seu punho parece uma caverna enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.53,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.17,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)Jumping Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.47,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Arm Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.40,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:03.02,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.42,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Deixe-me te dar uma mão!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:06.21,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sanji, conto com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.60,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Arume do Rēru... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.52,Main,Chopper,0, 0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kokutei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.87,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rozeo Shūto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:26.41,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Seu bastardo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:31.32,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Por que você insiste em atacar o mesmo lugar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.39,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Se não funcionou antes, não funcionará agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:35.77,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Vai funcionar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.54,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,, A dor é um sinal para proteger o corpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:41.59,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Não tê-la... não o torna mais forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.83,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Diga o que quiser então!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.57,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Ei, é perigoso, vocês dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.47,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Saiam rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:51.04,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.24,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Droga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.89,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.42,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gatoringu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:02.57,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.98,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.60,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Mais dois...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.80,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Todo mundo... está sendo eliminado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.36,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.81,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Quatro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.45,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Cinco!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.12,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,E só restam três!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:45.02,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Só... restam três.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:54.20,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Agora, apresse-se e esmague-os, Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.27,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ele está chegando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:02.78,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,É inútil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.38,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Não podemos vencer um monstro desses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Estamos sem opções!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:08.65,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O que devemos fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:10.58,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.12,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Vou criar uma abertura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.07,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.79,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Tudo bem então!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.66,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,O que você quer dizer, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.66,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.82,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pisutoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.14,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.87,Secondary,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Santōryū...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.33,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Yasha Garasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:45.62,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Conseguimos!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.68,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Funcionou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.82,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Usopp, agora{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.58,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Atacando meu braço direito de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.36,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Eu já te disse inúmeras vezes; não vai funcionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.25,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Eu vou me livrar de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.80,Thoughts,Zoro,0,0,0,,Ele desapareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:06.72,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.38,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ei, Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.25,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Olhe para cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.06,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.09,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Algo... entrou na minha boca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.14,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Usopp, o que foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:29.63,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Eu consegui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.53,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Eu finalmente consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:35.46,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Finalmente fiz Oars engolir o sal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.66,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.29,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,E daí?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.85,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Entendo, você não sabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:43.34,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Sal é a fraqueza do zumbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.81,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Olha! É o fim para o Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A sombra de Luffy está saindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.25,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Purifique-se, zumbi monstruoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:59.11,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A vitória é minha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Saia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.86,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Por que... a sombra de Moria...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.15,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Estou protegendo ele de dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.80,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Que simplório.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.71,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Comemorando a vitória prematuramente.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:36.00,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Você realmente achou que eu não teria uma contramedida para tal fraqueza?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.56,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.34,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.57,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Acho que isso é seu, narigudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.39,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.98,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nada bom, o sal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.62,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O sal que o Brook juntou para nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.94,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Droga! Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.22,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Tirando sarro da gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:08.23,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.90,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sutanpu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.07,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:21.97,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:24.81,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:25.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.72,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.37,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.60,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.47,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Ainda não!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.05,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Esmague-o em pedaços!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:38.07,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,O mesmo vale para a mulher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.63,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Esmague-os! Esmague-os!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:52.17,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Esmague cada um deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:55.87,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Esmague aqueles que já estão inconscientes também!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.13,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Ainda tem um pouco de fôlego neles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:03.68,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Esmague-os até que não sejam mais reconhecíveis como humanos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:14.06,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Ei, grande idiota.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:20.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,O que você acha que está pisando?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:29.50,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Ninguém está sob seus pés.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.81,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.73,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Eu... Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.02,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Eu fui salvo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.07,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Não sei o que aconteceu, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.57,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Obrigado por nos ajudar aqui{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.09,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.23,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.48,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,L-Lu{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.58,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Lu{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.50,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Luffy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.28,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Qual parte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:03.85,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Você meio que...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Você meio que se parece com ele, mas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.01,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,É você mesmo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Você tá falando sério!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Sou... realmente eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.32,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Bem, sua maneira de falar combina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.79,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:21.37,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Ele também tem a habilidade de se transformar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.79,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Ou...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Todos foram derrotados?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.47,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,S-Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:34.18,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Exceto nós, todos os outros foram espancados por aquele monstro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.25,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.17,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Saia da frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.84,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Saia da frente!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.62,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Você não entendeu, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:43.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Aquele zumbi possui sua sombra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Além disso, seu corpo pode se esticar e executar suas técnicas também!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.46,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Não importa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.22,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Esmague-os, Oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.35,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.93,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:02.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Aí vem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.17,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raifuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.68,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,O único Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.02,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,sou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.62,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Algo está voando para cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.36,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,O que é?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.26,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Uma nuvem de chuva?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:32.26,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.73,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,É o Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.19,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.69,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.52,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Ele está conseguindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.41,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Ele está lutando de igual para igual com o Oz!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.81,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Agora é nossa chance! Comecem a procurar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.58,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,E-Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:21.55,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Encontrei um membro da Tripulação da Esperança!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.51,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Aqui também!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.62,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Que ferimento horrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.32,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Todos foram espancados violentamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.74,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Esse cara foi espancado a ponto de seus ossos ficarem visíveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.92,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,É perigoso deixá-los aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.76,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Leve-os para algum lugar seguro, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.01,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O que eles estão fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.00,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,São tantos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.62,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Eles são zumbis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O que eles vão fazer com Zoro e os outros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.69,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.21,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.82,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.75,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Oars está perdendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:54.98,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Não acredito que um monstro desses esteja perdendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:04.67,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,O que houve, O-Oars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.41,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Ei! Você ouviu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:14.43,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Moriah-sama está atualmente dentro da barriga de Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:22.81,Main,zombie,0,0,0,,Então, o mestre de todos os zumbis em Thriller Bark está sendo derrotado, junto com o Zumbi Especial supremo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.28,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Que tipo de piada é essa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:32.20,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Oars... o homem lendário que há 500 anos era chamado de demônio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.20,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,E nosso mestre é um Shichibukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.92,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Gekko Moriah-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:55.64,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Então, ao encher o Luffy com as sombras de 100 vítimas, você o fez ficar assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:58.67,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo, Tripulação da Esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:02.23,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Para ser honesto, estamos surpresos com o quanto de poder ele adquiriu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:06.20,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Mas... essa força só vai durar mais 2 ou 3 minutos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.87,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,As sombras que colocamos nele começarão a deixar seu corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.86,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Lamentamos por mexer com seu capitão, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.93,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Nós confiamos a ele toda a nossa esperança!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.83,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Queremos ser humanos novamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.15,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Ele é nossa última esperança!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.22,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Está quase amanhecendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:28.21,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,O destino de todas as vítimas da ilha será decidido nos próximos minutos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:32.58,Main,Lola,0,0,0,,Contamos com você, Luffy Pesadelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.49,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,A mansão está se despedaçando!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:52.90,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.65,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Isso é realmente incrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.24,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Muito bem, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.83,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Seu bastardo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.62,Main,Oz,0,0,0,,Escória insignificante!
